#: ../../developer-guide/architecture/data-structures.en.rst:44
msgid ""
"Data transfer driver. This contains a set of *producers*. Each producer "
"is connected to one or more *consumers*. The tunnel handles events and "
"buffers so that data moves from producers to consumers. The data, as much"
" as possible, is kept in reference counted buffers so that copies are "
"done only when the data is modified or for sources (which acquire data "
"from outside |TS|) and sinks (which move data to outside |TS|)."
msgstr ""

